00:00:23.859 --> 00:00:28.600
in blackjack the goal is to beat the
dealer the player wins if his hand as a

00:00:28.600 --> 00:00:31.279
higher value than the dealers without
going bust

00:00:31.279 --> 00:00:34.519
the player also wins if the dealer busts
and the player doesn't

00:00:34.519 --> 00:00:38.290
busting is when the total value of the
hand goes over 21

00:00:38.290 --> 00:00:41.900
and when players bust they automatically
lose regardless of whether the dealer

00:00:41.900 --> 00:00:42.790
busts as well

00:00:42.790 --> 00:00:47.710
next you need to learn the card values
